                <Class>
                    <__p_name>BlockFactory</__p_name>
                    <__p_description>This is the singleton block factory class. It creates new blocks. It loads new languages by importing their module and registering their block types during the load process. It provides a list of languages and block types per language.

It creates new blocks. Blocks can be created by language and type or the root type of a language.</__p_description>
