                <Class>
                    <__p_name>ParserModel</__p_name>
                    <__p_description>This is the singleton parser model class. It handles execution of a given abstract parser. A slot is provided for starting a new abstract parser. Signals are provided for informing when parsing begins, makes progress, finishes, and has remaining unknown code fragments. This class is designed to run on its own thread because parsing can be a long process. Because of this the GUI must interface with this class exclusively through its signals and slots.</__p_description>
                    <__p_parents>qtc.QObject</__p_parents>
                    <__p_infile>0</__p_infile>
                    <Function>
