                <Class>
                    <__p_name>ProjectView</__p_name>
                    <__p_description>This is the project view class. It provides the main tree view for a project model. Actions are provided for all basic editing actions done upon this view's model.

It provides the main tree view for a project model. A view acts as the primary view for an entire project, allowing the user to navigate and view any part of the project tree. It provides a context menu that contains all actions a view can do upon its project model. The context menu provided fills the role of a main window's edit menu.

Actions are provided for all basic editing actions done upon a view's model. These actions allow the user to edit the project tree with undo, redo, add, remove, cut, copy, paste, move up, and move down actions. For adding and pasting into the project an option is provided to insert before, into, or after the currently selected block. The individual qt actions are also provided if they need to be added to another custom menu or toolbar. The provided actions are enabled or disabled based off the current state of a view.</__p_description>
                    <__p_parents>qtw.QTreeView</__p_parents>
