Preprocessor header lines scanned from the given input file, assuming it is at the beginning of the file. This will include the header guard lines if the given input file is a C++ header.</__p_returnDescription>
                        <__p_static>0</__p_static>
                        <__p_abstract>0</__p_abstract>
                        <Object>
                            <__p_name>ifile</__p_name>
