                <Class>
                    <__p_name>Scanner</__p_name>
                    <__p_description>This is the parser scanner class. It provides an object oriented scanner for an input file given to it at initialization. This scans python lines of code, skipping blank lines. It keeps track of the block of code it is scanning by the indent, stopping once a smaller indent is encountered.</__p_description>
                    <__p_infile>0</__p_infile>
