The next line of python source code read in from this scanner's input file. If the end of file is reached or the end of the code block with the determined indent then this returns none. The first time this is called the indent of the block to be read is determined with the first line of code encountered.</__p_returnDescription>
                        <__p_static>0</__p_static>
